Off the top of my head I think this might be due to which particular server you play on?<br>
Anyway... this isnt my point.<br>
My point is that as a Merc I personally feel I lack a group enhancement.<br>
I could list all the classes in Alb and their skills but you guys already know that stuff.<br>
I personally think that as a class we dont bring ANYTHING benificial to a group.<br>
Our damage output is &quot;equalled&quot; by armsmen who have the benifit of wearing plate armour. They run outa endurance but we can get a Paladin to compensate for that... Reaver quite handy cos they can keep the stealthers off the casters. And their damage aint too shaby either. Friars good too cos they can heal at a push and some of their buffs really are good. Minstral.. well thats a given.... run buffs and a bit of CC if the casters get swamped, plus mana regen...<br>
My point is what do Mercs bring to the party? Even our assigned role of being caster killers falls by the wayside when our &quot;special ability&quot; of Dirty Tricks doesnt work on casters. And everyone seems to have a PBAOE caster with them these days.<br>
I could take on enemy tanks but then again Mythic has informed me I shouldnt win against them.<br>
Can anyone tell me what roll im supposed to play in an RvR group? Why should groups WANT me? In large scale RvR lag and slowdown is so bad I can barely get my positional styles off.<br>
